1. Moj prijatelj ima problema sa zdravljem. (*problemima*) (My friend has health problems.)
2. Srbija se suočava sa ekonomskim problemima. (*problemima*) (Serbia is facing economic problems.)
3. Naš tim se uspešno nosi sa svim problemima koji se javljaju. (*problemima*) (Our team is successfully dealing with all the problems that arise.)
4. Problemima ne treba bežati, već ih treba rešavati. (*problemima*) (You shouldn't run away from problems, but solve them.)
5. Škola organizuje tribinu o problemima u obrazovanju. (*problemima*) (The school is organizing a panel on problems in education.)
6. Problemi u braku su normalna pojava. (*problemima*) (Marital problems are a normal occurrence.)
7. Učenici se suočavaju sa mnogim problemima u savladavanju gradiva. (*problemima*) (Students face many problems in mastering the material.)
8. Rešavanje ekoloških problema zahteva zajednički rad. (*problemima*) (Solving environmental problems requires teamwork.)
9. Nekim ljudima teško padaju veliki društveni problemi. (*problemima*) (Some people have a hard time dealing with big social problems.)
10. Problemima možemo pristupiti na različite načine. (*problemima*) (We can approach problems in different ways.)